      "config": {
        "actionKey": "",
        "actionBindings": [],
        "actionInstructionBlocks": {},
        "taskInstruction": "输出 capability_review JSON、capability_gap JSON 和 capability_builder_handoff JSON。capability_review 说明 found=false、reason、direct_response_strategy，并把 needs_another_capability 设为 false。capability_gap 必须包含 gap_detected(true)、gap_type(action|graph_template|unknown)、reason、missing_capability、suggested_asset_type(action|graph_template|none)、build_requirement、should_offer_build(boolean)、should_route_to_builder(boolean)。只有用户明确要求创建、补齐、以后具备某能力，或 request_understanding 表明目标就是构建能力时，should_route_to_builder 才为 true；普通任务缺能力时只 should_offer_build=true，交由最终回复询问用户。\n\ncapability_builder_handoff 必须包含 handoff_ready(boolean)、target_kind(action_creation_workflow|graph_template_creation_workflow|none)、target_template_id(string)、target_available(boolean)、build_request(markdown string)、requires_user_confirmation(true)、source_gap(object)、user_visible_next_step(string)。当 suggested_asset_type=action 且 should_route_to_builder=true 时，target_template_id 必须是 toograph_action_creation_workflow 且 target_available=true；当 suggested_asset_type=graph_template 且 should_route_to_builder=true 时，target_kind 使用 graph_template_creation_workflow，target_template_id 必须是 toograph_graph_template_creation_workflow 且 target_available=true；不允许假装已经创建能力。",
        "modelSource": "global",
        "model": "",
        "thinkingMode": "high",
        "temperature": 0.1
      }
    },
